{"tid":1510335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［要走佬就快］美國要打冷戰既話，係樂意見到香港收皮","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T15:26:42.000Z","uid":40250,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99346d3b2058ffe59bf2a767392b9f35ee435ea1","tid":1510335,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:52:34.000Z","msg":"如果美國要打冷戰逼使國際資本離開中國，佢地係樂意見到香港呢個資本窗口收皮。咁美國以外既國家都無一個安全地方做中國生意，自然會流走。<br />\n<br />\n我地希望美國持續施壓，逼到中國接受貿易協議開放市場，同時就會由得香港自生自滅。 但問題係中國只要開放市場就等於經濟崩潰，亡黨之路，中共政權會寧願鎖國全民食屎都唔會妥協。<br />\n<br />\n照咁睇香港真係死路一條，但係香港有為數唔少既人都係有攬住中國炒既心態。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我角度睇，10月1前唔走資去離岸戶口同走人，一齊炸死既機會非常高。無心理準備共存亡既人，或者屋企人，盡快收拾行裝同資產，先行離開香港"},{"pid":"70543a0713363bfc68fd803f1cb12367465bf5bd","tid":1510335,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=bd830acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=d4835f67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=2383b2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"e241efaa4fa45c4f70c9d609deef2220f40234ef","tid":1510335,"uid":40250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:54:02.00